<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/useraccount.css">
    <title>User Account</title>
</head>
<body>
    <section class="user-account">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>User Account</h1>
            <p>Allows users to create an account with login details, providing a personalized experience and secure access to their financial information.</p>
            <div class="cards">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-image">
                        <!-- Add image here -->
                        <img src="/images/secure.png" alt="Secure Access">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Secure Access</h3>
                    <p>Our platform ensures the highest level of security to protect your financial information. Rest assured that your data is safe with us.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-image">
                        <!-- Add image here -->
                        <img src="/images/person.png" alt="Personalized Experience">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Personalized Experience</h3>
                    <p>Create a unique user account and customize your personal finance management system according to your preferences. Tailor your budgeting tools, expense tracking, and financial goals to suit your needs.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-image">
                        <!-- Add image here -->
                        <img src="/images/login.png" alt="Easy Login">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Easy Login</h3>
                    <p>Access your account with ease using your login details. Enjoy a seamless experience every time you visit our website.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

